 The Washington Post last week. =E2=80=9CPeople are just stupid.=E2=80=9D</=
p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I don=E2=80=99t get it either.=
=C2=A0We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2580=
6429.278654/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTg=
